description:
Raw data for &ldquo;Quantitative reconstitution of RNA processing bodies&rdquo; 

 Raw data for the preprint/article &ldquo;Quantitative reconstitution of RNA processing bodies&rdquo; are included here. These data are primarily raw micrographs that were collected by the authors using confocal microscopy for this study. Please see preprint for details on data collection or how the data were processed: https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2022.08.13.503854v1 

 Micrographs can be opened and processed using FIJI or ImageJ: https://fiji.sc/ 

 &nbsp;

